channel.title: Botting Soul Wars
channel.description:
I am botting soul wars, aiming for 70 attack, 80 str, and 60 def. I currently have: 60 attack 59 str. 56 def.
Approximately how long will it take me with 12 hours botting a day?

item.dc:creator: @Frell Frell
item.description:
@Frell wrote:

xp from 59-80/xp for 1 point = total points needed
total points x20 = minutes(/2 if majority are wins)
minutes/60 = total hrs of bottin’

Its late, that might not by right. But remember that the xp for each point will change as you lvl.
